 189:../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/dev/mpr121.h ****     /** Read the filtered data from channel t. The ADC raw data outputs
 190:../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/dev/mpr121.h ****         run through 3 levels of digital filtering to filter out the high
 191:../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/dev/mpr121.h ****         frequency and low frequency noise encountered. For detailed information on
 192:../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/dev/mpr121.h ****         this filtering see page 6 of the device datasheet.
