 219:../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/dev/mpr121.h ****         of a sensor. For example, if bit 0 is set then channel 0 of the
 220:../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/dev/mpr121.h ****         device is currently deemed to be touched.
 221:../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/dev/mpr121.h ****     */
 222:../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/dev/mpr121.h ****     uint16_t Touched()
